206
00:15:58.124 --> 00:16:00.094
This is Elizabeth Wright.
head of station in Rome.

207
00:16:00.168 --> 00:16:02.878
I've got a message
from James Greer.

208
00:16:02.962 --> 00:16:05.132
What? He's still kicking?

209
00:16:05.215 --> 00:16:08.835
