you. Officer Wright.

212
00:16:28.822 --> 00:16:30.952
Are you ready?

213
00:16:50.385 --> 00:16:52.465
You're not going with him?

214
00:16:52.554 --> 00:16:56.774
It is his journey
alone. You are with me.

215
00:17:08.445 --> 00:17:11.405
[tires screeching]

216
00:17:11.489 --> 00:17:14.199
